{"tid":160681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中五生睇會德豐MONTEREY　趁熱鬧見大場面","createTime":"2017-03-18T02:45:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-18T02:45:45.000Z","uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a989053e218d3aa9607023e59c43fc92e8f10735","tid":160681,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T02:45:45.000Z","msg":"會德豐地產將軍澳MONTEREY正展開B組銷售程序，吸引同區家庭客到場。一位身穿童軍服裝的中五學生林同學稱，今日放學後便陪家人前往售樓處抽籤「睇大場面」，坦言「本身諗住抽唔到，但抽中咗」。<br />\n<br />\n被問及本地樓價情況，他表示，現時樓價都幾貴吓，而今日主要陪家人抽籤，故自己未有理會該盤「賣幾錢一呎」。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170317/bkn-20170317193050517-0317_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20170317%2Fbkn-20170317193050517-0317_00842_001.html&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6v1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=5ac84f5e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170317/bkn-20170317193050517-0317_00842_001.html</a>"}]}